                --------------------------------
                Change the look of BubbleStones
                --------------------------------


With BubbleStones you have the possibility to change the look of the Game.
You can make your "look file". See the file "MakeLook.iff" for more informations.

In information window of BubbleStones.info enter the tooltype "LOOK=lookname".

Available "lookname" :

LOOK=arena



